                <persName type="authority">Rāmakr̥ṣṇa</persName>
              </author>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīmatparamahaṃsaparivrājakācāryaśrībhāratītīrthavidyāranyamunivarya kiṃ kareṇa śrīrāmakṛṣṇākhyaviḍaṣāviracite brahmānaṃde 'dvaitānaṃdonāmatṛtīyodhyāyaḥ // (f. 13v).</colophon>
